Enid Markey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Enid_Markey 0 Enid Markey (February 22, 1894 – November 15, 1981) was an American actress of theater, film, and television. She originated the role of Jane in films, having twice played the character - in 1918 (Tarzan of The Apes; The Romance of Tarzan).
